### Register a new driver
POST http://localhost:3000/drivers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "driver123",
  "name": "John Doe"
}

### Accept a ride
POST http://localhost:3000/drivers/accept-ride
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "driverId": "driver123",
  "rideId": "ride123"
}

### Complete a ride
POST http://localhost:3000/drivers/complete-ride
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "driverId": "driver123",
  "rideId": "ride123",
  "fareAmount": 50
}
